p-sided loaf tin, pastry brush, wire rack, airtight container, oven","hintsAndTricks":["Serve fresh or toasted with your favourite jam, butter or spread.","Proving time may vary depending on time of year and ambience. Choose a warm, dark place to leave dough to prove and try covering the loaf tin with a towel to insulate if necessary. Leave for further 15 - 30 minutes if not doubled in size, a maximum of 45 - 60 minutes should be sufficient.","Mill 40 g dried chickpeas in step 1 with rice and millet to make your own chickpea flour."],"basicInfo":["medium","10m","1h 10m","12 slices"]}